org.overture.interpreter.scheduler

Class InitThread

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.overture.interpreter.scheduler.InitThread
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISchedulableThread

    public class InitThread
extends Object
implements ISchedulableThread
    This class is used as a wrapper class for the main Java thread which initializes VDM, it should now be used in the VDM evaluation.

    kela
